# pt_BR: Brazilian Portuguese keeps all vowel diacritics (ГЎ Г  Гў ГЈ, Г© ГӘ,
# Гӯ, Гі Гҙ Гө, Гә, Гј) and the cedilla on Г§ вҖ” every one is phonemic in either
# vowel quality (ГЎ /a/ vs Гў /Йҗ/), stress, or marks nasalization (ГЈ, Гө).
# Both lexicon and OOV inputs are NFC by construction.
#
# Apostrophe and hyphen survive `[^-.'[:L:]]` and pass to the G2P; the
# trained model learns them as letter tokens (mostly silent / epsilon).

:: NFC ;
:: Any-Lower ;
:: Null ;
:: [^-.'[:L:]] Remove ;
